    "title": "Lawyer: E-Discovery/Document Review",
    "displayTitle": "Lawyer: E-Discovery/Document Review",
    "body": "<p>The AI is trained on thousands of past litigation documents to recognize <strong>patterns</strong> associated with <i>relevance</i> (e.g., all emails referencing \"unauthorized payment\" or \"confidential\"). It quickly flags millions of documents for human review.</p>",
