    "title": "New Component Title",
    "displayTitle": "New Component Title",
    "body": "<p>The AI is trained on rubrics and past student essays to recognize <strong>patterns</strong> in grammar, structure, and style. It provides instantaneous feedback on a draft's fluency and coherence, freeing the teacher to focus on content and critical thinking.</p>",
