    "title": "New Component Title",
    "displayTitle": "New Component Title",
    "body": "<p>The AI uses real-time user behavior data (clicks, purchases, demographics) to recognize <strong>patterns</strong> that maximize conversion. It automatically adjusts bidding amounts, target audiences, and even creative placement <i>without</i> human intervention.</p>",
