    "title": "New Component Title",
    "displayTitle": "New Component Title",
    "body": "<p>The AI is trained on vast amounts of published content. It recognizes <strong>patterns</strong> in article structures, tone, and flow to generate detailed outlines or complete first drafts of blog posts, emails, or technical documentation based on a simple prompt.</p>",
