    "_isResetOnRevisit": "false",
    "_isA11yCompletionDescriptionEnabled": true,
    "title": "New Component Title",
    "displayTitle": "New Component Title",
    "body": "<p>The power of these use cases comes from AI's incredible <strong>Speed &amp; Scale</strong>, processing vast data instantly. However, this power comes with inherent limitations that demand careful human interaction:</p><ul><li><strong>Weakness: Lacks Context/Common Sense:</strong> AI focuses on <strong>patterns</strong> in the data, not real-world <i>meaning</i> or <i>causality</i>.</li><li><strong>Weakness: Prone to Hallucinations:</strong> Generative AI predicts the most likely next word, which often results in outputs that sound plausible but are <strong>factually incorrect or fabricated</strong>.</li><li><strong>Weakness: Data Dependency &amp; Bias:</strong> If the training data is biased, incomplete, or contains errors (<strong>Garbage In, Garbage Out / GIGO</strong>), the AI will replicate and amplify that bias.</li></ul>",
    "_ariaLevel": 0,
