    "body": "<p><meta></p><p style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:12pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#1f1f1f;\"><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Artificial Intelligence (AI) refers to computer systems designed to </strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>mimic human intelligence</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong> to perform specific tasks. Think of AI as an advanced tool that can see patterns, make decisions, or create content based on the data it's been trained on.</strong></span></b></span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#1f1f1f;\"><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Key Point:</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong> AI is not magic, and it is not a sentient being. Today, we exclusively use </strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>Narrow AI</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>, which means the system is only intelligent within a highly focused domain.</strong></span></b></span></p>",
